; Tests JVM spec requirement: interface must be declared abstract
; Expected warning: JVMS-001 (interface without abstract)
; This proves:
;   1. Parser detects interface flag without abstract flag
;   2. Warning message is clear and references JVM spec
;   3. Bytecode is still generated (warning, not error)

.class interface EmptyClass
.super java/lang/Object

.class_end
